---
title: Garlic Herb Butter Shrimp & Lobster with Lemony Broccoli & Chive Crème Fraîche Mashed Potatoes
description: No need to make a reservation at a fancy restaurant—bring the white tablecloth vibes to your dinner table with this surf ’n’ surf dish. Lobster tails are basted with a rich, garlic herb butter, which is also used to top spiced shrimp. The crustacean celebration is paired with lemony roasted broccoli, plus an epic twist on your traditional mashed potatoes. Our secret? We blend in butter, chives, and a generous dollop of crème fraîche for ultimate silky goodness. Bon appétit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61d4c552b9a7cb4e245a79b8-b4c72b0e.jpg
